title: Power Rankings #2: Chiefs & Chargers rise; Cowboys free fall; 49ers process
itunes:title: Power Rankings #2: Chiefs & Chargers rise; Cowboys free fall; 49ers process
description:
The NFL Power Rankings podcast with Colleen Wolfe and Dan Hanzus begins looking at the San Francisco 49ers surprising loss against the Chicago Bears. Dan shares why you shouldn't overreact to the 49ers loss and then he explains why it was an easy choice to put the Chiefs high in his week-2 power rankings. The Los Angeles Rams got rocked against the Buffalo Bills on opening night but Dan thinks it's important to relax on the Rams after week-1. Later on, Dan shares which team is his power move, he owns up to his mistakes, and then he explains why the Steelers are the hardest team to figure out after week-1.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
